title: Batan Waru
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Has some vegetarian dishes. Jun 2014 update: Kafe Batan Waru moved down the road and is a temporary food bazaar upstairs and out the front of Lippo Mall whilst the renovation for its new cafe is being finished. Also has a cafe in Ubud.
streetAddress: Jalan Kartika Plaza, Lippo Mall, Lippo Mall Kuta
